The paper deals with the segmentation of organs in medical images, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The specific application of the segmentation is in medical imaging (cs.Medical Imaging) and radiation treatment planning (cs.RO).
